        "body": "After opening devotions, you should help the children to finish memorizing the prayer\nintroduced in Lesson 4.1. Remember that they will start to learn a new prayer in the next set,\nso you should make sure they can recite the one from this set well. You will also want to\ncontinue to look for opportunities to discuss with your students how the spiritual qualities of\njustice, love, radiance, and compassion relate to the theme of living in harmony with others and\nhave them recite the corresponding verses they know, when appropriate."
